# Vite build output. Regenerated by `npm run build` in frontend/ and rebuilt
# from scratch inside the Docker image on every `fly deploy`, so it should
# never be tracked. The build output sits inside src/kinder_blockly/ so that
# the python package_data rule `static/**/*` ships it with the wheel — that
# is also how the production container serves the SPA at /.
src/kinder_blockly/static/
